<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894>
    dc:creator "Barboza, Gloria E.", "Knapp, Sandra", "Saerkinen, Tiina" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "A revision of the South American species of the Morelloid clade (Solanum L., Solanaceae)" ;
    bibo:endPage "342" ;
    bibo:journal "PhytoKeys" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2023-08-29" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "231" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure15>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure16>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure17> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure15>
    dc:description "Figure 15. Solanum americanum A habit B detail of abaxial leaf surface C detail of adaxial leaf surface D branch with inflorescence E leaf F dissected flower G fruit (A-D, F, G Cremers 8084 E Farrugia et al. 2773). Illustration by R. Wise. Previously published in Saerkinen et al. (2018: 57) and Knapp et al. (2019: 38)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897476" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure16>
    dc:description "Figure 16. Solanum americanum A habit B leaves and young inflorescence C buds and flowers D mature, shiny black fruits with reflexed calyx lobes (A, D Knapp et al. 10210 B Knapp et al. 10205 C Knapp et al. 10360). Photos by S. Knapp. Previously published in Saerkinen et al. (2018: 58) and Knapp et al. (2019: 39)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897477" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure17>
    dc:description "Figure 17. Distribution map of Solanum americanum in South America. For distribution elsewhere, see Saerkinen et al. (2018: 60) and Knapp et al. (2019: 43)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897478" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

